race.comment: FUN TO LOVE NZ (1) is in good form at present. Finished fourth at her latest appearance over 2240m at Melton, beaten 5 metres. Likely to get all the favours from this nice draw. Has the ability to take this out. SABINE (3) has been racing well of late. Finished fourth at her latest appearance over 2090m at Hobart, beaten 6 metres. No excuses from this advantageous draw. This should be an easier assignment so she is a major player. SMOKESCREEN (4) has to come into calculations on the back of some strong recent form, most recently when fourth at Hobart over 2090m. Must be included. KARALTA ARTEMIS (8) cannot be ruled out but needs a bit of luck from the tricky draw.
